Chile May Balance Fiscal Account, Post Surplus, Larrain Says

-- B y   R a n d y   W o o d s
-- 
2011-06-28T18:08:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/chile-may-balance-fiscal-account-post-surplus-larrain-says.html
Chile’s government may balance its
fiscal account or post a small surplus this year, Finance
Minister Felipe Larrain said in a speech in  London  today.  Chile’s economic growth will exceed 6 percent this year, he
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
